**═══════════════════════════════════════**

**Overall Influence:** [+ camarilla_strength +]/100
[? if camarilla_strength >= 80 : *(Complete control - Hindenburg is their puppet)* ?]
[? if camarilla_strength >= 60 and camarilla_strength < 80 : *(Strong influence - they filter all information)* ?]
[? if camarilla_strength >= 40 and camarilla_strength < 60 : *(Moderate influence - they shape his views)* ?]
[? if camarilla_strength < 40 : *(Limited influence - Hindenburg still independent)* ?]

